### HandyCrafts Adapter - Enhanced Availability and Payment Testing

### 1. Check Product Availability (New POST method)
POST https://localhost:7777/api/adapter/availability
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "HC-1001",
  "quantity": 2
}

### 2. Check Product Availability (Legacy GET method)
GET https://localhost:7777/api/adapter/availability/HC-1001

### 3. Process Payment with Quantity
POST https://localhost:7777/api/adapter/payments/HC-1001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 1,
  "customerInfo": "John Doe - john@example.com"
}

### 4. Get Payment History
GET https://localhost:7777/api/adapter/payments/history

### 5. Get Current Product Inventory
GET https://localhost:7777/api/adapter/products/inventory

### 6. Check availability for low stock item
POST https://localhost:7777/api/adapter/availability
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "HC-1004",
  "quantity": 1
}

### 7. Process payment for low stock item
POST https://localhost:7777/api/adapter/payments/HC-1004
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 1,
  "customerInfo": "Jane Smith - jane@example.com"
}

### 8. Try to buy more than available stock (should fail)
POST https://localhost:7777/api/adapter/availability
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "HC-1004",
  "quantity": 5
}